window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>The weakest hunter of all mankind!</b></p> <p>E-rank hunter Jinwoo Sung has no money, no talent, and no prospects to speak of - and apparently, no luck, either! When he enters a hidden double dungeon one fateful day, he’s abandoned by his party and left to die at the hands of some of the most horrific monsters he’s ever encountered.</p> <p>But just before the last, fatal blow...<i>ping! </i>[Congratulations on becoming a Player.]</p>"; 
